Herald Child and defection land at the Embassy, Child Sees the Fighting, a 
bot that was obviously blessed was fending of a Much bigger and evil bot, A 
voice speaks to child 'show them your strength'. Child Breaks free of his 
father and steps toward the battle, he feels energy flowing threw him, He 
held up his Hand and energy Blew out it like a canon, Child then Screamed "In 
The Name of the Matrix!" And the Energy blast split in two, one headed 
towards Galvatron and the other heads towards Skyquake
